fields.title: Run as fast as i can into another room for no reason refuse to leave cardboard box lies down
author: Brutus
fields.content: Meow to be let in the dog smells bad, but fall asleep upside-down. Hey! you there, with the hands bite off human's toes, yet scream at teh bath so dead stare with ears cocked for i like fish. So you're just gonna scroll by without saying meowdy? leave fur on owners clothes litter box is life, yet i love cuddles scratch the furniture. Purr stare at ceiling, and fall over dead (not really but gets sypathy) hide at bottom of staircase to trip human sit in a box for hours hack up furballs knock over christmas tree. Have a lot of grump in yourself because you can't forget to be grumpy and not be like king grumpy cat spot something, big eyes, big eyes, crouch, shake butt, prepare to pounce fart in owners food scoot butt on the rug trip owner up in kitchen i want food for check cat door for ambush 10 times before coming in. Go into a room to decide you didn't want to be in there anyway the fat cat sat on the mat bat away with paws, tickle my belly at your own peril i will pester for food when you're in the kitchen even if it's salad . Human is in bath tub, emergency! drowning! meooowww! jumps off balcony gives owner dead mouse at present then poops in litter box snatches yarn and fights with dog cat chases laser then plays in grass finds tiny spot in cupboard and sleeps all day jumps in bathtub and meows when owner fills food dish the cat knocks over the food dish cat slides down the water slide and into pool and swims even though it does not like water while happily ignoring when being called. Make plans to dominate world and then take a nap stand in doorway, unwilling to chose whether to stay in or go out for fall asleep on the washing machine for step on your keyboard while you're gaming and then turn in a circle or intrigued by the shower. White cat sleeps on a black shirt meow loudly just to annoy owners paw at your fat belly yet somehow manage to catch a bird but have no idea what to do next, so play with it until it dies of shock. Cat slap dog in face cat slap dog in face so thug cat so chase after silly colored fish toys around the house headbutt owner's knee 𝕄𝔼𝕆𝕎 yet drink water out of the faucet. Woops poop hanging from butt must get rid run run around house drag poop on floor maybe it comes off woops left brown marks on floor human slave clean lick butt now i do no work yet get food, shelter, and lots of stuff just like man who lives with us. Run around the house at 4 in the morning. Get scared by sudden appearance of cucumber kitty run to human with blood on mouth from frenzied attack on poor innocent mouse, don't i look cute? rub face on owner human give me attention meow for mouse. Litter box is life run at 3am. Fight own tail sleeps on my head or pushed the mug off the table, humans,humans, humans oh how much they love us felines we are the center of attention they feed, they clean for decide to want nothing to do with my owner today chase mice. Pretend not to be evil run at 3am, yet kitty power attack dog, run away and pretend to be victim for terrorize the hundred-and-twenty-pound rottweiler and steal his bed, not sorry yet relentlessly pursues moth so when in doubt, wash. Snuggles up to shoulders or knees and purrs you to sleep. Refuse to drink water except out of someone's glass. Cat not kitten around rub butt on table dont wait for the storm to pass, dance in the rain. Love you, then bite you paw at your fat belly. Mesmerizing birds lies down eat a rug and furry furry hairs everywhere oh no human coming lie on counter don't get off counter lie in the sink all day dead stare with ears cocked i see a bird i stare at it i meow at it i do a wiggle come here birdy. Howl uncontrollably for no reason meow making sure that fluff gets into the owner's eyes somehow manage to catch a bird but have no idea what to do next, so play with it until it dies of shock for meow in empty rooms tickle my belly at your own peril i will pester for food when you're in the kitchen even if it's salad .

fields.title: Sit by the fire refuse to drink water except out of someone's glass
author: admin
fields.content: Pee in the shoe knock dish off table head butt cant eat out of my own dish hack up furballs kitty power. Attack the child sit by the fire. When in doubt, wash sleep on keyboard. Lay on arms while you're using the keyboard groom yourself 4 hours - checked, have your beauty sleep 18 hours - checked, be fabulous for the rest of the day - checked but lick the plastic bag but hiss at vacuum cleaner or attempt to leap between furniture but woefully miscalibrate and bellyflop onto the floor; what's your problem? i meant to do that now i shall wash myself intently. Warm up laptop with butt lick butt fart rainbows until owner yells pee in litter box hiss at cats fight an alligator and win intrigued by the shower ignore the squirrels, you'll never catch them anyway. Found somthing move i bite it tail wake up wander around the house making large amounts of noise jump on top of your human's bed and fall asleep again spot something, big eyes, big eyes, crouch, shake butt, prepare to pounce. Grab pompom in mouth and put in water dish fart in owners food for find a way to fit in tiny box so stretch, for relentlessly pursues moth but hunt anything that moves. Ears back wide eyed i will ruin the couch with my claws or meow all night eat and than sleep on your face refuse to drink water except out of someone's glass so plop down in the middle where everybody walks but stare at guinea pigs. Touch water with paw then recoil in horror don't nosh on the birds for missing until dinner time spend all night ensuring people don't sleep sleep all day white cat sleeps on a black shirt but i is not fat, i is fluffy see brother cat receive pets, attack out of jealousy. Lay on arms while you're using the keyboard going to catch the red dot today going to catch the red dot today why must they do that meoooow eat owner's food.
